### ExpenseTracker API — end-to-end walkthrough
### Works with the VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client.
###
### Run the requests top-to-bottom. After Login, copy the token from the
### response into the @token variable below so every protected request works.

@host = http://localhost:5027

# ── Paste the token from the Login response here ─────────────────────────────
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

# Set these after creating the resources below
@categoryId = PASTE_CATEGORY_ID_HERE
@expenseId  = PASTE_EXPENSE_ID_HERE
@budgetId   = PASTE_BUDGET_ID_HERE


### ── 1. Register ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "Password1",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### ── 2. Login — copy the "token" from the response into @token above ─────────
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "Password1"
}

### ── 3. Create a category ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy the "id" from the 201 Location header into @categoryId above
POST {{host}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Groceries",
  "color": "#4CAF50"
}

### ── 4. List categories ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 5. Create an expense ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy the "id" from the 201 Location header into @expenseId above
POST {{host}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 47.50,
  "description": "Weekly shop",
  "date": "2025-03-15T10:00:00Z",
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}"
}

### ── 6. List expenses (paginated) ───────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/api/expenses?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 7. Filter expenses by date range ───────────────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/api/expenses?from=2025-03-01&to=2025-03-31&categoryId={{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 8. Get a single expense ────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/api/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 9. Update an expense ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
PUT {{host}}/api/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 53.20,
  "description": "Weekly shop (updated)",
  "date": "2025-03-15T10:00:00Z",
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}"
}

### ── 10. Create a budget ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy the "id" into @budgetId above
POST {{host}}/api/budgets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "limitAmount": 200.00,
  "month": 3,
  "year": 2025,
  "alertThresholdPercentage": 80
}

### ── 11. List budgets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/api/budgets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 12. Monthly summary (cached, 5 min TTL) ────────────────────────────────
# Shows per-category spending vs budget with alert flags
GET {{host}}/api/reports/monthly-summary?month=3&year=2025
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 13. Delete the expense (should invalidate the summary cache) ────────────
DELETE {{host}}/api/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 14. Monthly summary again — reflects the deletion instantly ─────────────
GET {{host}}/api/reports/monthly-summary?month=3&year=2025
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 15. Validation error example (400 Problem Details) ─────────────────────
POST {{host}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": -5,
  "description": "",
  "date": "2099-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### ── 16. Not found example (404 Problem Details) ────────────────────────────
GET {{host}}/api/expenses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── 17. Update a budget ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PUT {{host}}/api/budgets/{{budgetId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "limitAmount": 300.00,
  "alertThresholdPercentage": 75
}

### ── 18. Update a category ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
PUT {{host}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Food & Groceries",
  "color": "#8BC34A"
}
